data.title: Justin Timberlake
data.meta_description: Justin Randall Timberlake is an American singer, songwriter, record producer, actor and dancer. Timberlake first became famous when he appeared in the television series Mickey Mouse Club. He later became part of the Grammy Award-winning boy band NSYNC. He started his own career as a solo musician in 2002. As a solo he sold 90 Million albums with 4 albums and with NSYNC nearly 80 Million with 3 albums.
data.text: Justin Randall Timberlake (born January 31, 1981) is an American singer, songwriter, record producer, actor and dancer. Timberlake first became famous when he appeared in the television series Mickey Mouse Club. He later became part of the Grammy Award-winning boy band NSYNC. He started his own career as a solo musician in 2002. As a solo he sold 90 Million albums with 4 albums and with NSYNC nearly 80 Million with 3 albums.
